('6aabc438-84e6-5010-aeba-019d5ec01d37', 'e510adb6-1da1-40d9-8350-4be6be0cf60d', 'SENIOR_HIGH', '___ kind of music do you enjoy listening to?', '你喜歡聽什麼樣的音樂？', 'what', 'which', 'some', 'any', '限定詞 (形容詞用法)', 'what 後面常接名詞來詢問「種類」。', '2026-07-05 12:27:18', '2026-07-05 12:27:18');
